#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Usually program messages and documentation are written in English. Using a "
"framework made of a set of tools and libraries, it is possible to have your "
"favorite applications speak your native non-English language. This process "
"of adapting an application to a specific language is known as "
"<emphasis>localization</emphasis>. The localization process includes "
"translating the program's interfaces and documentation to the various "
"languages users need and, in some countries or regions, making the inputs "
"and outputs conform to particular conventions. &lokalize; is a tool which "
"will assist you in the localization process to make an application's "
"interface speaks many languages."
msgstr ""
"通常程序消息和文档都是用英文编写的。通过使用由一系列工具和库组成的框架，可以"
"让您喜爱的应用程序使用您的非英语母语。这种使应用程序适应特定语言的过程称为"
"<emphasis>本地化</emphasis>。本地化过程包括将程序界面和文档翻译成用户所需的各"
"种语言，并在某些国家或地区使输入输出符合特定惯例。&lokalize; 是一个工具，将协"
"助您完成本地化过程，使应用程序界面能够使用多种语言。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every internationalization-aware program makes available for translation one "
"or more message-catalog files. The extension of these files is <filename "
"class=\"extension\">.pot</filename>. <acronym>POT</acronym> is an acronym "
"for <quote>Portable Object Template</quote>. &lokalize; is an advanced and "
"easy to use PO file (&GNU; gettext message catalogs) editor. It is a "
"computer-aided translation system for translators, written from scratch "
"using the &kde; Platform 4 framework. Aside from basic editing of PO files "
"with nifty auxiliary details, it integrates support for glossary, "
"translation memory, diff-modes for QA, project managing, &etc; It has many "
"features like full navigation capabilities, extensive editing functionality, "
"search functions, syntax checking and statistics functions."
msgstr ""
"每个具有国际化意识的程序都会提供一个或多个可供翻译的消息目录文件。这些文件的"
"扩展名为 <filename class=\"extension\">.pot</filename>。<acronym>POT</"
"acronym> 是 <quote>便携式对象模板</quote> 的缩写。&lokalize; 是一个先进且易用"
"的 PO 文件（&GNU; gettext 消息目录）编辑器。它是一个为翻译人员设计的计算机辅"
"助翻译系统，完全基于 &kde; Platform 4 框架开发。除了提供带有巧妙辅助细节的 "
"PO 文件基本编辑功能外，它还集成了术语表、翻译记忆库、质量检查的差异模式、项目"
"管理等支持。它具有许多功能，如完整的导航能力、广泛的编辑功能、搜索功能、语法"
"检查和统计功能。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Portable Object (.po) files: Each translator takes a copy of one of these "
"POT templates and begins to fill in the blanks: each message is translated "
"into the language desired. The file containing the translated text is "
"referred to as a PO (Portable Object) file."
msgstr ""
"便携式对象 (.po) 文件：每位翻译人员会获取这些 POT 模板之一的副本并开始填写空"
"白：每条消息都被翻译成所需的语言。包含翻译文本的文件称为 PO（便携式对象）文"
"件。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editor"
msgstr "编辑器"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main Window"
msgstr "主窗口"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, the main window contains six parts. The upper-right box is read-"
"only and contains the current msgid (source text) field from the opened PO-"
"file. The edit box just below this contains the msgstr (target text) field "
"related to the msgid shown and here you can input or edit the translated "
"text."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，主窗口包含六个部分。右上方的窗格为只读区域，显示当前打开的 PO 文"
"件中 msgid（源文本）字段的内容。紧邻其下方的编辑框则对应所显示 msgid 的 "
"msgstr（目标文本）字段，您可在此输入或编辑翻译文本。"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "The main default &lokalize; window"
msgstr "默认的 &lokalize; 主窗口"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "This shows the default window when a file is opened."
msgstr "此图显示了打开文件时的默认窗口。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The top-left part of the main window shows the Translation Units. Below "
"this, there is Unit Metadata section and it contains comments relevant to "
"the currently displayed source text. In the lower-left, there is a "
"Translation Memory section which shows the suggested translations from the "
"translation memory database for the current source text entry. On the lower-"
"right corner of the window, the glossary section is shown."
msgstr ""
"主窗口的左上部分显示翻译单元。其下方是单元元数据部分，包含与当前显示的源文本"
"相关的注释。左下角是翻译记忆库部分，显示翻译记忆库数据库中针对当前源文本条目"
"的建议翻译。窗口的右下角显示术语表部分。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Translation files are opened in separate tabs, with two big multi-line edits "
"as well as a bunch of <emphasis>tool views</emphasis>. These views can be "
"stacked (similar to tabs), shown separately, or hidden. Translation files "
"consist of many English-target pairs called <emphasis>units</emphasis>. A "
"<emphasis>unit</emphasis> typically correspond to a single string in the "
"user interface, or one paragraph in the documentation. The purpose of the "
"first multi-line edit is to display the original part of the pair. The "
"purpose of the second multi-line edit is to display the translation. You can "
"navigate through the <emphasis>units</emphasis> via the "
"<guilabel>Translation Units</guilabel> view or by using <keycap>Page Down</"
"keycap> and <keycap>Page Up</keycap>."
msgstr ""
"翻译文件在单独的标签页中打开，带有两个大的多行编辑框以及一些<emphasis>工具视"
"图</emphasis>。这些视图可以堆叠（类似于标签页）、单独显示或隐藏。翻译文件包含"
"许多称为<emphasis>单元</emphasis>的原文-目标语对。一个<emphasis>单元</"
"emphasis>通常对应界面中的单个字符串或文档中的一个段落。第一个多行编辑框的目的"
"是显示原文部分，第二个多行编辑框的目的是显示译文。您可以通过 <guilabel>翻译单"
"元</guilabel> 视图或使用 <keycap>Page Down</keycap> 和 <keycap>Page Up</"
"keycap> 在<emphasis>单元</emphasis>之间导航。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A unit may be <emphasis>translated</emphasis> or <emphasis>untranslated</"
"emphasis>. A translation of a translated unit may be <emphasis>ready</"
"emphasis> or <emphasis>not ready</emphasis> (also called <emphasis>fuzzy</"
"emphasis> sometimes). If the unit is not ready, its translation is rendered "
"in italics. &lokalize; allows you to easily navigate through the file "
"according to the state of their translation. See <guilabel>Go</guilabel> "
"menu for the shortcuts. The status bar at the bottom of the window shows the "
"current string number, total number of strings, total untranslated strings, "
"total not ready (fuzzy) strings and status of the current string "
"respectively. When navigating, untranslated units are treated as not ready. "
"Also, you may use the filtering feature of <guilabel>Translation Units</"
"guilabel> toolview. Pressing <keycap>Page Down</keycap> actually takes you "
"to the next unit in filtered/sorted list of that tool view."
msgstr ""
"一个单元可能处于<emphasis>已翻译</emphasis>或<emphasis>未翻译</emphasis>状"
"态。已翻译单元的译文可能标记为<emphasis>就绪</emphasis>或<emphasis>未就绪</"
"emphasis>（有时也称为<emphasis>模糊</emphasis>）。若单元未就绪，其译文会以斜"
"体显示。&lokalize; 允许您根据翻译状态轻松浏览文件，具体快捷键请参阅 "
"<guilabel>跳转</guilabel> 菜单。窗口底部的状态栏会分别显示当前字符串编号、字"
"符串总数、未翻译字符串数、未就绪（模糊）字符串数以及当前字符串状态。在导航"
"时，未翻译单元会被视为未就绪状态。此外，您还可以使用 <guilabel>翻译单元</"
"guilabel> 工具视图的筛选功能——按下 <keycap>Page Down</keycap> 实际上会跳转到"
"该工具视图筛选/排序列表中的下一个单元。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To ease up translation of the console applications where spacers in messages "
"are important you can check the <guilabel>Visualize separators such as "
"spaces, tabs and new lines in the editor</guilabel> item on the page "
"<guilabel>Editing</guilabel> of the configuration window which can be opened "
"by choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &lokalize;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> main "
"menu item."
msgstr ""
"为简化控制台应用程序的翻译工作（此类应用中消息的间距符至关重要），您可勾选配"
"置窗口 <guilabel>编辑</guilabel> 页面中的 <guilabel>在编辑器中可视化显示空"
"格、制表符和换行符等分隔符</guilabel> 选项。该配置窗口可通过主菜单 "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>设置</guimenu><guimenuitem>配置 &lokalize;...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> 打开。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have no access to the original translation template file (it is a "
"common practice on some commercial translation projects) then you can use a "
"translation file from the related language. Just choose the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Clear all translated "
"entries</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item or use <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Alt;"
"<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> shortcut to clear all translation units."
msgstr ""
"若您无法获取原始翻译模板文件（某些商业翻译项目的常见情况），可使用相关语言的"
"翻译文件作为基础。只需选择 <menuchoice><guimenu>文件</guimenu><guimenuitem>清"
"除所有已翻译条目</guimenuitem></menuchoice> 菜单项，或使用 <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> 快捷键即可清空所有翻译单元。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To the main window one can add many more sections like <guilabel>Alternate "
"Translations</guilabel>, <guilabel>Primary Sync</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Secondary Sync</guilabel>, <guilabel>Binary Units</guilabel> by "
"using <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Toolviews</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the main menu."
msgstr ""
"通过主菜单 <menuchoice><guimenu>设置</guimenu><guimenuitem>工具视图</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>，用户可为主窗口添加更多功能区块，例如 <guilabel>备"
"选翻译</guilabel>、<guilabel>主同步视图</guilabel>、<guilabel>次同步视图</"
"guilabel>、<guilabel>二进制单元</guilabel>。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbars"
msgstr "工具栏"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add or remove actions in the toolbars using "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Toolbars...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the main menu."
msgstr ""
"通过主菜单 <menuchoice><guimenu>设置</guimenu><guimenuitem>配置工具栏...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> 可自定义工具栏中的动作项。"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure Toolbars"
msgstr "配置工具栏"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you can configure the toolbars."
msgstr "此处可进行工具栏配置。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information read the section about <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"config.html#toolbars\">Toolbars</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"更多信息请阅读 &kde; 基础指南中关于<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/config."
"html#toolbars\">工具栏</ulink>的章节。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcut keys"
msgstr "快捷键"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can save time by using shortcut keys during translation. To configure "
"shortcut keys, use <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from "
"the main menu."
msgstr ""
"翻译过程中使用快捷键可有效节省时间。如需配置快捷键，请通过主菜单 "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>设置</guimenu><guimenuitem>配置快捷键...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> 进行设置。"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure Shortcuts"
msgstr "配置快捷键"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you can configure the shortcut keys."
msgstr "此处可配置快捷键。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information read the section about <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"config.html#shortcuts\">Shortcuts</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"更多信息请阅读 &kde; 基础指南中关于<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/config."
"html#shortcuts\">快捷键</ulink>的章节。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Tips"
msgstr "通用技巧"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are doing translations for &kde;, then either you will already have "
"&lokalize; project file in your language folder (usually named "
"<filename>index.lokalize</filename>), or you can select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Project</guimenu><guimenuitem>Create new project</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> and the wizard will download translation files for "
"your language and will create project for you."
msgstr ""
"若您正在为 &kde; 进行翻译，您的语言文件夹中可能已存在 &lokalize; 项目文件（通"
"常命名为 <filename>index.lokalize</filename>），或者您可以选择 "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>项目</guimenu><guimenuitem>创建新项目</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>，向导将自动下载您所需语言的翻译文件并为您创建项目。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is recommended that you get used to the keyboard shortcuts instead of the "
"menus and toolbars for increased productivity. For example, use the "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> to focus <guilabel>Quick "
"search</guilabel> input line to filter the unit list in "
"<guilabel>Translation Units</guilabel> view. Once you are done, press "
"<keycap>Page Down</keycap> to start moving along the filtered list. Pressing "
"<keycap>Esc</keycap> in the filter input will move the focus back to the "
"target text field without selecting another unit."
msgstr ""
"建议您习惯使用键盘快捷键而非菜单和工具栏，以提高工作效率。例如，使用 "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> 聚焦至 <guilabel>快速搜索</"
"guilabel> 输入行，以筛选 <guilabel>翻译单元</guilabel> 视图中的单元列表。操作"
"完成后，按 <keycap>Page Down</keycap> 沿筛选后的列表移动。在筛选输入框中按 "
"<keycap>Esc</keycap> 将使焦点返回至目标文本字段，且不会选择其他单元。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are working with translation files in XLIFF format (definitely the "
"case when you translate OpenDocument), then extended states are available "
"(<emphasis>new</emphasis>, <emphasis>needs review</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>approved</emphasis>, &etc;). You may select them in drop-down menu "
"of <guilabel>Approved</guilabel> button in the toolbar. Classification of "
"the state as <emphasis>ready</emphasis> or <emphasis>not ready</emphasis> "
"depends on the current <emphasis>workflow phase</emphasis> "
"(<emphasis>translation</emphasis>, <emphasis>review</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>approval</emphasis>). A default phase for you depends on your "
"<emphasis>role</emphasis> in the project (set in project settings). Each "
"unit usually contains information about phase it was changed last time, and "
"for each phase its owner is logged to the file."
msgstr ""
"若您处理的是 XLIFF 格式的翻译文件（翻译 OpenDocument 时必然遇到），则可使用扩"
"展状态（<emphasis>新增</emphasis>、<emphasis>需要复审</emphasis>、<emphasis>"
"已核准</emphasis>等）。您可通过工具栏 <guilabel>已核准</guilabel> 按钮的下拉"
"菜单选择这些状态。状态归类为 <emphasis>就绪</emphasis> 或 <emphasis>未就绪</"
"emphasis> 取决于当前<emphasis>工作流阶段</emphasis>（<emphasis>翻译</"
"emphasis>、<emphasis>复审</emphasis>、<emphasis>核准</emphasis>）。您的默认阶"
"段取决于项目中设置的<emphasis>角色</emphasis>（在项目设置中配置）。每个单元通"
"常包含其最后修改阶段的信息，且每个阶段的操作者都会被记录至文件中。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "Projects"
msgstr "工程"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Notes"
msgstr "通用提示"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The projects are one of the main concepts in &lokalize;. A project is "
"represented by a file that contains paths, folders with translations, "
"templates, and other files: glossary file, automation scripts, translation "
"memories. Whenever &lokalize; opens a file without a project loaded, it will "
"search for a project file in the parent folders (up to four levels). "
"Alternatively, you can specify the project file via the <userinput>--"
"project</userinput> flag when starting &lokalize; from the command line."
msgstr ""
"项目是 &lokalize; 的核心概念之一。项目通过文件形式呈现，其中包含路径、翻译文"
"件夹、模板及其他文件：术语表文件、自动化脚本、翻译记忆库。当 &lokalize; 在未"
"加载项目的情况下打开文件时，会在父级文件夹中（最多向上四级）搜索项目文件。您"
"也可通过命令行启动 &lokalize; 时使用 <userinput>--project</userinput> 参数指"
"定项目文件。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each project you select your role in it (<emphasis>translator</"
"emphasis>, <emphasis>reviewer</emphasis>, <emphasis>approver</emphasis>), "
"which in turn affects the workflow phase &lokalize; automatically picks up "
"for files you edit."
msgstr ""
"对于每个项目，您需要选择在其中担任的角色（<emphasis>翻译员</emphasis>、"
"<emphasis>复审员</emphasis>、<emphasis>核准员</emphasis>），这将影响 "
"&lokalize; 为您编辑的文件自动选取的工作流阶段。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to define a word wrapping position on a project level. Just "
"use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Project</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure "
"project...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item then go to the "
"<guilabel>Advanced</guilabel> page."
msgstr ""
"可在项目层级定义自动换行位置。只需通过 <menuchoice><guimenu>项目</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>配置项目...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> 菜单项，进入 <guilabel>高"
"级</guilabel> 页面进行设置。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Translation memories (unlike project files, glossary and scripts) are not "
"shared between the translation team members, as they are created and stored "
"under the user's home folder, meaning that the translation memories for all "
"of the projects are stored in the same folder and thus can be used when "
"other projects are opened."
msgstr ""
"翻译记忆库（与项目文件、术语表和脚本不同）不会在翻译团队成员间共享，它们创建"
"并存储于用户主文件夹下，这意味着所有项目的翻译记忆库均存储于同一文件夹，因此"
"在打开其他项目时亦可调用。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Project Overview tab"
msgstr "项目概览标签页"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start &lokalize; first time, you will see an empty "
"<guilabel>Project Overview</guilabel> tab. Project Overview is a file "
"manager view, which helps you keep an overview of your PO files. The "
"&lokalize; suite will help you to translate quickly and also to keep "
"translations consistent. &lokalize; workflow implies that you start with "
"creating/opening a project."
msgstr ""
"首次启动 &lokalize; 时，您将看到空白的 <guilabel>项目概览</guilabel> 标签页。"
"项目概览是一个文件管理器视图，可帮助您统览所有 PO 文件。&lokalize; 套件将助您"
"高效完成翻译并保持译文一致性。&lokalize; 的工作流程建议从创建/打开项目开始。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new project, use <menuchoice><guimenu>Project</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Create new project</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This "
"will guide through the steps to create a new project. In <guimenu>Project</"
"guimenu> menu you can also find options like <guimenuitem>Project overview</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Configure project</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Open project</guimenuitem>, and <guimenuitem>Open recent "
"project</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"要创建新项目，请使用 <menuchoice><guimenu>项目</guimenu><guimenuitem>创建新项"
"目</guimenuitem></menuchoice>。这将引导您完成新项目创建的各个步骤。在 "
"<guimenu>项目</guimenu> 菜单中，您还可找到 <guimenuitem>项目概览</"
"guimenuitem>、<guimenuitem>配置项目</guimenuitem>、<guimenuitem>打开项目</"
"guimenuitem> 及 <guimenuitem>打开最近项目</guimenuitem> 等选项。"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid "Project Overview Tab"
msgstr "项目概览标签页"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you can configure the project."
msgstr "此处可配置项目。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Project Overview</guilabel> tab displays a file tree with "
"statistics for a current project, such as the percentage of translated units "
"completed and the last translator. It allows you to open a selected file in "
"a new tab of the current &lokalize; window."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>项目概览</guilabel> 标签页以文件树形式显示当前项目的统计信息，例如"
"已翻译单元的完成百分比和最后一位翻译人员。您可通过此视图在当前 &lokalize; 窗"
"口的新标签页中打开选定文件。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can switch off the completely translated files from the "
"<guilabel>Project Overview</guilabel> using the <guibutton>Hide completed "
"items</guibutton> button on the main toolbar or <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>T</"
"keycap></keycombo> default shortcut."
msgstr ""
"您可使用主工具栏上的 <guibutton>隐藏已完成项</guibutton> 按钮或默认快捷键 "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo>，在 <guilabel>项目概览</"
"guilabel> 中隐藏已完全翻译的文件。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start &lokalize; the next time it will show the last opened file by "
"default. You can switch off this behavior with the <guilabel>Restore the "
"previously opened files when opening &lokalize;</guilabel> item on the page "
"<guilabel>General</guilabel> of the configuration window which can be opened "
"by choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &lokalize;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> main "
"menu item. The same page can be used to configure &lokalize; behavior when "
"you switch to the next/previous tab in it. It is possible to go through the "
"tab list according to the tab positions or according to their activation "
"order."
msgstr ""
"下次启动 &lokalize; 时，默认将显示最后打开的文件。您可通过配置窗口 <guilabel>"
"常规</guilabel> 页面中的 <guilabel>打开 &lokalize; 时恢复先前打开的文件</"
"guilabel> 选项关闭此行为。该配置窗口可通过主菜单 <menuchoice><guimenu>设置</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>配置 &lokalize;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> 打开。同一"
"页面还可配置 &lokalize; 在切换下一个/上一个标签页时的行为，支持按标签页位置或"
"按激活顺序进行跳转。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid "Glossary"
msgstr "词汇表"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Have you ever become tired of typing the same long text sequence several "
"times just because it would take more time to find its translation for a "
"copy and paste? Now you will only have to find the (frequent) word sequence "
"in the <guilabel>Glossary</guilabel> view, and then insert it by pressing a "
"shortcut."
msgstr ""
"您是否曾因重复输入长文本序列而感到疲惫？尽管查找其译文进行复制粘贴可能更耗"
"时。现在，您只需在 <guilabel>术语表</guilabel> 视图中找到（常用）词语序列，然"
"后通过快捷键即可插入。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Of course the glossary should be populated with word sequences first. "
"&lokalize; has a handy glossary editor that allows an explicit search over "
"the entire glossary."
msgstr ""
"当然，术语表需先填充词语序列。&lokalize; 提供便捷的术语表编辑器，支持对整个术"
"语表进行精确搜索。"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>Glossary view in the bottom right corner displays glossary "
"entries appropriate for the current unit</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>右下角的术语表视图显示适用于当前单元的术语表条目</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>Glossary view in the bottom right corner displays glossary entries "
"appropriate for the current unit</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>右下角的术语表视图显示适用于当前单元的术语表条目</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid "Translation Memory"
msgstr "翻译存储"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Translation Memory</guilabel> view allows you to drag and drop "
"a folder with translation files from say &dolphin; into the view, and then, "
"within few minutes, translation suggestions will be shown automatically on "
"the unit switch. To insert the translation suggestions into the file, use "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>1</keycap></keycombo>, <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>2</"
"keycap></keycombo> and so on, depending on the number of suggestion."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>翻译记忆库</guilabel> 视图支持从 &dolphin; 等文件管理器拖拽翻译文件"
"文件夹至视图内，随后在几分钟内，切换单元时将自动显示翻译建议。要插入翻译建议"
"至文件，请使用 <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>1</keycap></keycombo>、"
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>2</keycap></keycombo> 等快捷键，具体取决于建议数量。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Manage translation "
"memories</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to add/manage projects to your "
"Translation Memory. Here you can also import or export data from <filename "
"role=\"extension\">tmx</filename> file format."
msgstr ""
"使用 <menuchoice><guimenu>工具</guimenu><guimenuitem>管理翻译记忆库</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> 可向翻译记忆库添加/管理项目。此处还可导入或导出 "
"<filename role=\"extension\">tmx</filename> 格式的数据。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing <keycombo><keycap>F7</keycap></keycombo> will open "
"<guilabel>Translation Memory</guilabel> tab, which allows you to query the "
"TM freely. Clicking a search result will open the corresponding file and "
"unit. If you want to quickly open some file in the project (and it is added "
"to TM), then instead of browsing <guilabel>Project Overview</guilabel> you "
"can just type its name into the <guilabel>File mask</guilabel> field, "
"accompanied by '*'."
msgstr ""
"按下 <keycombo><keycap>F7</keycap></keycombo> 将打开 <guilabel>翻译记忆库</"
"guilabel> 标签页，支持自由查询翻译记忆库。点击搜索结果将打开对应文件及单元。"
"若需快速打开项目中的某个文件（且该文件已添加至翻译记忆库），无需浏览 "
"<guilabel>项目概览</guilabel>，只需在 <guilabel>文件掩码</guilabel> 字段中输"
"入文件名（可配合使用 '*' 通配符）。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The TM engine indexes all entries, including non-ready and untranslated "
"ones. This allows it to completely replace the Search-in-Files feature which "
"required scanning every file in the project each time a search is done."
msgstr ""
"翻译记忆库引擎会索引所有条目（包括未就绪和未翻译的条目），这使其能完全取代“在"
"文件中搜索”功能——该功能每次搜索都需要扫描项目中的每个文件。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The outdated TM entries will be deleted from the &lokalize; translation "
"memory on rescan or clicking a missing entry if you check the "
"<guilabel>Delete missing files from translation memory on Rescan or when "
"clicking a missing entry</guilabel> item on the page <guilabel>Translation "
"Memory</guilabel> of the configuration window which can be opened by "
"choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure "
"&lokalize;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> main menu item."
msgstr ""
"若勾选配置窗口 <guilabel>翻译记忆库</guilabel> 页面中的 <guilabel>在重新扫描"
"或点击缺失条目时从翻译记忆中删除缺失文件</guilabel> 选项，过时的翻译记忆库条"
"目将在重新扫描或点击缺失条目时从 &lokalize; 翻译记忆库中删除。该配置窗口可通"
"过主菜单 <menuchoice><guimenu>设置</guimenu><guimenuitem>配置 &lokalize;...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> 打开。"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>&lokalize; with translation memory search results for the "
"current unit</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&lokalize; 显示当前单元的翻译记忆库搜索结果</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>&lokalize; with translation memory search results for the current "
"unit</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&lokalize; 显示当前单元的翻译记忆库搜索结果</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid "Batch Translation:"
msgstr "批量翻译："

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To insert the exactly matching suggestion automatically from the translation "
"memory database, use <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Fill "
"in all exact suggestions</guimenuitem></menuchoice> OR <guimenuitem>Fill in "
"all exact suggestions and mark as fuzzy</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"要自动插入翻译记忆库中完全匹配的建议，请使用 <menuchoice><guimenu>工具</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>填充所有精确建议</guimenuitem></menuchoice> 或 "
"<guimenuitem>填充所有精确建议并标记为模糊</guimenuitem>。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid "Translation Synchronization Capabilities"
msgstr "翻译同步功能"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Sync Mode</guilabel> (previously known as <guilabel>Merge "
"Mode</guilabel>) saves a great deal of time for the editors, and for cases "
"when two or more translators are working simultaneously on the same file, or "
"when one has to maintain translations for several branches of software."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>同步模式</guilabel>（先前称为<guilabel>合并模式</guilabel>）为编辑"
"人员节省大量时间，适用于以下场景：两名或多名翻译人员同时处理同一文件，或需要"
"维护软件多个分支的翻译。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&lokalize; allows quick navigation through units that differ, and displays "
"word-by-word differences. Also, &lokalize; has two Sync views - "
"<guilabel>Primary Sync</guilabel> and <guilabel>Secondary Sync</guilabel>. "
"They are identical, but the former is usually used to merge translations and "
"second to keep in sync translations for two software branches."
msgstr ""
"&lokalize; 支持快速导航至存在差异的单元，并显示逐词差异对比。此外，"
"&lokalize; 提供两个同步视图——<guilabel>主同步视图</guilabel> 与 <guilabel>次"
"同步视图</guilabel>。两者功能相同，但前者通常用于合并翻译，后者则用于保持两个"
"软件分支的翻译同步。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After you copied translation from auxiliary file (<emphasis>synchronized</"
"emphasis> it), any subsequent changes made to this unit will be replicated "
"back to auxiliary file."
msgstr ""
"当您从辅助文件复制翻译（即<emphasis>同步</emphasis>操作）后，对该单元所做的任"
"何后续更改都将同步回辅助文件。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid "Merging"
msgstr "合并"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One use of <guilabel>Sync Mode</guilabel> is reviewing changes made by (new) "
"contributors, when you cannot be sure of the quality of the work done."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>同步模式</guilabel> 的一个应用场景是审阅（新）贡献者所做的修改，当"
"您无法确定其工作质量时。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open a base file, then drop its changed version into the <guilabel>Primary "
"Sync</guilabel> view, followed by <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>Down</keycap></"
"keycombo> or <keycombo>&Alt; <keycap>Up</keycap></keycombo> (remember that "
"shortcuts may be modified in a usual way for all &kde; applications) to "
"navigate through entries that are different."
msgstr ""
"打开基准文件后，将其修改版本拖放至 <guilabel>主同步视图</guilabel>，随后使用 "
"<keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>Down</keycap></keycombo> 或 <keycombo>&Alt; "
"<keycap>Up</keycap></keycombo>（请注意，所有 &kde; 应用程序的快捷键均可按常规"
"方式修改）在不同条目间导航。"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>&lokalize; used for merging changes in translation</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&lokalize; 用于合并翻译更改的界面</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&lokalize; used for merging changes in translation</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&lokalize; 用于合并翻译更改的界面</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replication"
msgstr "同步复制"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Sync Mode</guilabel> may also be used to make changes to "
"translation for two branches simultaneously. Set <guilabel>Branch folder</"
"guilabel> path in your project options to the path that corresponds to base "
"folder of the branch, and <guilabel>Secondary Sync</guilabel> view will "
"automatically open files from branch. Then, each time you make changes in "
"files of your main branch, they will automatically be replicated to the "
"branch (of course, if it contains the same English string)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>同步模式</guilabel> 也可用于同时对两个分支的翻译进行修改。在项目选"
"项中设置 <guilabel>分支文件夹</guilabel> 路径为对应分支的基础文件夹路径，"
"<guilabel>次同步视图</guilabel> 将自动从分支打开文件。此后，每当您在主分支文"
"件中进行更改时，这些更改将自动同步至分支（当然，前提是分支包含相同的英文字符"
"串）。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example, if you work on &kde; translation, you can checkout trunk to "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/home/xx/hacking/kde/trunk/l10n-kf5/YOUR_LANG</"
"filename> and branch to <filename class=\"directory\">/home/xx/hacking/kde/"
"branches/stable/l10n-kf5/YOUR_LANG</filename>. Create &lokalize; project: "
"<filename>/home/xx/hacking/kde/trunk/l10n-kf5/YOUR_LANG/project.lokalize</"
"filename> and set <filename class=\"directory\">BranchDir=../../../branches/"
"stable/l10n-kf5/YOUR_LANG</filename>, then work via this project, and commit "
"changes in both trunk and branch folders."
msgstr ""
"例如，若您从事 &kde; 翻译工作，可将主干代码检出至 <filename class=\"directory"
"\">/home/xx/hacking/kde/trunk/l10n-kf5/您的语言</filename>，分支代码检出至 "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/home/xx/hacking/kde/branches/stable/l10n-kf5/"
"您的语言</filename>。创建 &lokalize; 项目：<filename>/home/xx/hacking/kde/"
"trunk/l10n-kf5/您的语言/project.lokalize</filename> 并设置 <filename class="
"\"directory\">BranchDir=../../../branches/stable/l10n-kf5/您的语言</"
"filename>，然后通过此项目进行工作，并提交主干和分支文件夹中的更改。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid "Alternate Translations"
msgstr "可选翻译"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each unit may have several <emphasis>alternate translations</emphasis> "
"associated with it. Such translations may appear during file update, when "
"the source string is slightly changed. In this case the old translation with "
"it's (old) source is moved to alternate translations list, so that they are "
"not lost."
msgstr ""
"每个单元可能关联多个<emphasis>备选翻译</emphasis>。此类翻译可能在文件更新时出"
"现，即源字符串发生轻微变动时。此时，旧翻译及其（旧）源文将移至备选翻译列表，"
"以避免丢失。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When translating software, usually gettext tools are used to prepare "
"translation files. When original text changes, gettext tools update "
"translation files and mark entries with changed original text as "
"<emphasis>fuzzy</emphasis> (or <emphasis>non-ready</emphasis> in other "
"terminology). They store previous original text so that translators could "
"see what changes exactly were made. &lokalize; simplifies the life of the "
"translator and highlights parts of the original text that were changed in "
"the <guilabel>Alternate Translations</guilabel> view."
msgstr ""
"翻译软件时，通常使用 gettext 工具准备翻译文件。当原文发生变更时，gettext 工具"
"会更新翻译文件，并将原文已修改的条目标记为<emphasis>模糊</emphasis>（或其他术"
"语中的<emphasis>未就绪</emphasis>）。它们会存储先前的原文，以便翻译人员查看具"
"体变更内容。&lokalize; 简化了翻译人员的工作流程，并在 <guilabel>备选翻译</"
"guilabel> 视图中高亮显示自上次审阅后发生变动的原文部分。"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>&lokalize; highlighting parts of original text that were changed "
"since translation was last reviewed</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&lokalize; 高亮显示自上次翻译审阅后发生变动的原文部分</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>&lokalize; highlighting parts of original text that were changed "
"since translation was last reviewed</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&lokalize; 高亮显示自上次翻译审阅后发生变动的原文部分</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid "External Tools"
msgstr "外部工具"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pology"
msgstr "Pology"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:456
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The interaction with <application>Pology</application> can be configured "
"using the page <guilabel>Pology</guilabel> of the configuration window which "
"can be opened by choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &lokalize;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> main "
"menu item."
msgstr ""
"可通过配置窗口的 <guilabel>Pology</guilabel> 页面配置与 <application>Pology</"
"application> 的交互，该窗口通过主菜单 <menuchoice><guimenu>设置</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>配置 &lokalize;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> 打开。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information, please refer to <ulink url=\"http://pology.nedohodnik."
"net/\">Pology homepage</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"更多信息请参阅 <ulink url=\"http://pology.nedohodnik.net/\">Pology 官方网站</"
"ulink>。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid "LanguageTool"
msgstr "LanguageTool"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:467
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<application>LanguageTool</application> offers spell and grammar checking of "
"your translation units."
msgstr ""
"<application>LanguageTool</application> 可对您的翻译单元进行拼写和语法检查。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure your custom <application>LanguageTool</application> server "
"using the page <guilabel>LanguageTool</guilabel> of the configuration window "
"which can be opened by choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &lokalize;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> main "
"menu item."
msgstr ""
"您可通过配置窗口的 <guilabel>LanguageTool</guilabel> 页面配置自定义 "
"<application>LanguageTool</application> 服务器，该窗口通过主菜单 "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>设置</guimenu><guimenuitem>配置 &lokalize;...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> 打开。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To utilize <application>LanguageTool</application> checking capabilities use "
"the <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Check this unit using "
"LanguageTool</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item or use <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> shortcut."
msgstr ""
"要使用 <application>LanguageTool</application> 的检查功能，请通过 "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>编辑</guimenu><guimenuitem>使用 LanguageTool 检查此单元"
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice> 菜单项或 <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>J</keycap></"
"keycombo> 快捷键进行操作。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information, please refer to <ulink url=\"https://languagetool.org/"
"\">LanguageTool homepage</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"更多信息请参阅 <ulink url=\"https://languagetool.org/\">LanguageTool 官方网站"
"</ulink>。"

